{"tid":249685,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【因……的國泰航空】傳今日裁總經理級員工　國泰回應：精簡架構尚未執行","createTime":"2017-05-19T13:17:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T13:18:40.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"641805228ce9dffa18d2b7f8ff8fff11aeb42ca8","tid":249685,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T13:17:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170519/large/1495197039_ad20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170519%2Flarge%2F1495197039_ad20.jpg&h=e10046be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國泰（293）早前公佈須精簡架構，今日有傳先向最高職級管理層開刀，包括總經理（GM）級別，下一波行動將裁減經理級以上員工，6月殺到後勤基層員工。國泰發言人回覆查詢時，表示最近已公佈將建立更精簡、能迅速應變及更完善的新管理架構，惟除已公佈資訊外，「尚未執行有關變動」，將在適當時候公佈有關變動，目前首要任務是與同事保持溝通。<br />\n<br />\n國泰航空早前公佈，預算裁減30%管理人員成本。市傳今日會向後勤員工進行大規模裁員。消息指今日先向包括GM（總經理）在內的level E最高職級管理層「開刀」，多個部門都要削減或取消GM人手，以節省開支。另一波裁員行動則下周一（22日）進行，主要是level C（經理級）或以上的員工，牽涉部門包括營業及市務部、會計等。至於屬level A及B的後勤的基層員工也不能倖免，料將於6月裁員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56716919&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170519\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56716919%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170519&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuAHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=e58858aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56716919%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170519&h=69e8ccf7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56716919&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170519</a>"},{"pid":"8e86106ce776dcd7b116f419d2d71f4e0aa1db04","tid":249685,"uid":113074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T13:18:40.000Z","msg":"多數都係雷聲大雨點小然後搵一個就快退休嘅人請佢食肥雞餐"}]}